sequenceDiagram
    participant User as User/CI
    participant K8sAPI as Kubernetes API<br/>6443/TCP HTTPS TLS1.2+
    participant Controller as Operator Controller<br/>SA Token Auth
    participant LlamaStack as Llama Stack Pod<br/>8321/TCP HTTP
    participant Provider as Inference Provider<br/>Ollama/vLLM/TGI
    participant Prometheus as Prometheus<br/>optional
    participant Proxy as kube-rbac-proxy<br/>8443/TCP HTTPS

    Note over User,Controller: Flow 1: LlamaStackDistribution Creation
    User->>K8sAPI: kubectl apply LlamaStackDistribution<br/>HTTPS TLS1.2+ kubectl/SA Token
    K8sAPI->>Controller: Watch notification<br/>ServiceAccount Token
    Controller->>K8sAPI: Create ServiceAccount<br/>6443/TCP HTTPS TLS1.2+
    Controller->>K8sAPI: Create RoleBinding<br/>6443/TCP HTTPS TLS1.2+
    Controller->>K8sAPI: Create PVC (10Gi)<br/>6443/TCP HTTPS TLS1.2+
    Controller->>K8sAPI: Create Deployment<br/>6443/TCP HTTPS TLS1.2+
    Controller->>K8sAPI: Create Service<br/>6443/TCP HTTPS TLS1.2+
    Controller->>K8sAPI: Create NetworkPolicy<br/>6443/TCP HTTPS TLS1.2+

    Note over Controller,LlamaStack: Flow 2: Health Check
    Controller->>LlamaStack: GET /providers<br/>8321/TCP HTTP no auth
    LlamaStack-->>Controller: Health status response<br/>8321/TCP HTTP
    Controller->>K8sAPI: Update CR status<br/>6443/TCP HTTPS TLS1.2+

    Note over User,Provider: Flow 3: Inference Request
    User->>LlamaStack: POST /v1/* (inference)<br/>8321/TCP HTTP no auth
    LlamaStack->>Provider: Forward request<br/>varies/TCP HTTP/gRPC
    Provider-->>LlamaStack: Inference result<br/>varies/TCP HTTP/gRPC
    LlamaStack-->>User: JSON response<br/>8321/TCP HTTP

    Note over Prometheus,Controller: Flow 4: Metrics Collection
    Prometheus->>Proxy: GET /metrics<br/>8443/TCP HTTPS Bearer Token
    Proxy->>Controller: Forward to localhost:8080<br/>HTTP no auth
    Controller-->>Proxy: Prometheus metrics<br/>HTTP
    Proxy-->>Prometheus: Secured response<br/>HTTPS TLS
